data.description: Improved price and $5,000 to the lucky buyer towards your closing costs or interest rate buy down! Buy now!! Discover the freedom of space outside HOA restrictions on this expansive 1.24-acre property, just minutes away from Suncoast Highway 589 and Highway 19. Positioned conveniently, you're only 15 minutes from the best deep-sea fishing spots in Aripeka or Hernando Beach. Step into a home that embodies comfort and versatility, complete with a fireplace, pool, lanai, garage, workshop, chicken coop with optional feathered friends, and a fenced yard offering both privacy and serenity. The heart of the home is a recently updated kitchen featuring gleaming stainless steel appliances, tiled floors, and a striking granite counter and backsplash. Revel in the intricate details of beautifully stained wood trim that adds character throughout. With two distinct living areas - a family room and a living room with a wood-burning fireplace - and three bedrooms, each with laminate floors and blinds on all windows, the layout is both practical and inviting. Practicality meets luxury with three baths and an interior laundry area, ensuring every aspect of daily life is accommodated. The back lanai and screened pool area provide the perfect setting for relaxation, all while overlooking the fenced backyard. Additional features include a spacious garage and workshop area, allowing ample space for parking RVs, trailers, and vehicles. Two carports cater to autos or boats, offering further flexibility. The property is adorned with a metal roof on all buildings, not just for durability but also for potential insurance savings. Stay cool while working in the garage/shop with the added window unit. This new year, seize the opportunity to make this special home yours - a haven that combines functionality, freedom, and a home to love for the ultimate living experience.
